<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Interview Invitation - Crimble.com</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .interview-details {
      background-color: white;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .interview-details p {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .preparation-tips {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .preparation-tips h3 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .preparation-tips ul {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .preparation-tips li {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .calendar-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #27ae60;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Interview Invitation</h1>
    <p>Position: {{jobTitle}}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello {{candidateName}},</h2>
      
      <p>We are pleased to invite you for an interview for the position of <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> at <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>.</p>

      <div class="interview-details">
        <h3>Interview Details</h3>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{interviewDate}}</p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{interviewTime}}</p>
        <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{interviewDuration}}</p>
        <p><strong>Type:</strong> {{interviewType}}</p>
        {{#if interviewLocation}}
          <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{interviewLocation}}</p>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if interviewLink}}
          <p><strong>Meeting Link:</strong> {{interviewLink}}</p>
        {{/if}}
      </div>

      <div class="preparation-tips">
        <h3>Preparation Tips</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Review the job description and your application materials</li>
          <li>Research {{companyName}} and its recent developments</li>
          <li>Prepare questions about the role and company</li>
          <li>Test your video/audio equipment if it's a virtual interview</li>
          <li>Dress professionally and arrive on time</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>Please confirm your attendance by clicking the button below:</p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{confirmationLink}}" class="button">Confirm Attendance</a>
      </div>

      {{#if calendarLink}}
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="{{calendarLink}}" class="calendar-button">Add to Calendar</a>
        </p>
      {{/if}}

      <p>If you need to reschedule or have any questions, please contact us as soon as possible.</p>

      <p>Our AI interview preparation tool is available to help you prepare for the interview. You can access it through your dashboard.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>{{interviewerName}}<br>{{companyName}} HR Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© 2024 Crimble.com. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This email was sent to {{candidateEmail}}. If you have any questions about this interview, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 